data.description: The Holidays are merry and bright and so is our latest listing.  Welcome to this beautiful three bedroom, two and a half bath home that is move in ready and gleaming with all the must haves!  The spacious home offers hardwood floors throughout all the living spaces.  The kitchen offers granite countertops, tile flooring, look through to the living area and a pantry.  The dining room has a beautiful view of the spacious backyard that's perfect for those who enjoy the outdoors.   The outdoor space offers a bricked lounge area with a fire pit.  There is a spacious outdoor storage shed for your yard tools or toys.  Relax indoors by the cozy wood burning fireplace set between gorgeous built ins perfect for decorating or displaying your own unique style. NO HOA! Let's make a deal this season and welcome you to a home you're sure to fall in love with.
